&lt;p&gt;Thank you for your interest in Zero! This is a place to share relevant information about your skills and interests as it relates to working with us. Please complete the general inquiry form accessible below. Our team will reach out should we have any opportunities that fit your skill set. We also recommend keeping an eye on our Careers page &amp;amp; social media for any future opportunities you may want to apply for directly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that submission through this form does not automatically add you as an applicant to open positions. If you are interested in Contract-based work, please complete our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.zero.nyc/careers/4648362005&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Contractor interest form here&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Zero Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Zero is a creative studio founded in NYC. Our intention is to create an environment where multidisciplinary teams can solve problems for progressive and contemporary brands. We aim to constantly re-evaluate what it’s like to work with a studio and provide a high degree of value and service to our clients and our team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our studio seeks an individual with a diverse background and the ability to succeed with a wide array of motivated and creative individuals. We believe that process is at the core of our success - and are continually seeking to evolve ours to get the most out of each engagement. The unique and complex problems that face our clients call for fresh and strategic thinkers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a Senior Project Manager, you will provide critical support in fulfilling the mission of Zero Studios with an opportunity to help challenge and define best practices. An entrepreneurial spirit and business-oriented focus are paramount. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This position plays a pivotal role in maintaining project health, including resource allocation planning, optimizing processes, and strategic planning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ll work directly with our Project Management Director &amp;amp; Account Director(s) to manage 3-6 accounts primarily focused on Marketing &amp;amp; Social Media. We are looking for someone who has a strong foundation in these areas and who is exceptionally organized, possesses strong communication skills, and has the passion to manage and add value to each phase of a project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your primary responsibility will be to create strategic workstream plans that ensure delivery against project goals on time, on budget, and within scope. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In this role, Zero is expecting a strategic, solution-oriented individual able to break down complex problems into actionable solutions within the scope of a project. You will serve as a guide to multi-disciplinary teams, shaping and refining processes that deliver on a project’s success. We expect this individual to provide high-quality client service while offering guardrails for the creative process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will be managing a broad range of tasks related to project planning and execution. Defining and implementing process efficiencies across internal operations as well as establishing relationships will be vital to your success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a Senior Project Manager, our expectation is that you approach the day-to-day with a positive and solutions-oriented mindset. We believe the traits of kindness, respect, and empathy are vital to the role and a high degree of emotional intelligence and strategic thinking will be keys to success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Roles &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
